  "content": "h, scope_id: &str) -> Result<()> {\n    let dir = scope_dir(data_dir, scope_id);\n    if dir.exists() {\n        std::fs::remove_dir_all(&dir)\n            .map_err(|e| CorviaError::Storage(format!(\"Failed to delete scope dir: {e}\")))?;\n    }\n    Ok(())\n}\n```\n\n### Step 5: Register module in lib.rs\n\nAdd to `crates/corvia-kernel/src/lib.rs`:\n\n```rust\npub mod knowledge_files;\n```\n\n\n### Step 6: Run tests to verify they pass\n\nRun: `cargo test -p corvia-kernel -- knowledge_files`\nExpected: ALL PASS\n",
